OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780016591
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales' brother-in-law
OL,4,Copposes public footpath at family home
OL,6,FThe Princess of Wales' brother-in-law
OL,7,Fhas told a planning inquiry the
OL,8,Fcouple's high public profile means
OL,9,Fthey need a higher level of security
OL,10,Fat their home, amid an ongoing row
OL,11,Fover public access to part of their
OL,12,Fdrive.
OL,14,FJames Matthews, who married Kate's
OL,15,Fsister Pippa in May 2017, installed an
OL,16,Felectric security gate at Barton
OL,17,FCourt, in West Berkshire, in September
OL,18,F2022, which blocked access to a
OL,19,Fpathway "used by the walking public
OL,20,Ffor decades", according to some locals.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780016591
OL,3,CPrincess of Wales' brother-in-law
OL,4,Copposes public footpath at family home
OL,6,FWalking group West Berkshire Ramblers
OL,7,Fthen applied for a "definitive map
OL,8,Fmodification order" in January 2023 to
OL,9,Frecognise a public footpath on the
OL,10,Fland, which West Berkshire District
OL,11,FCouncil investigated.
OL,13,FThe council found the route was
OL,14,F"reasonably alleged to exist as a
OL,15,Fpublic right of way" based on
OL,16,Fevidence, legislation and case law,
OL,17,Finquiry documents said.
OL,26,@oD@TOUpD@SO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,315,300,200,140,000,100
